## Cyclomatic Complexity Rankings (highest → lowest)

> **CC formula used:** 1 + one point for each `if`, `else if`, `for`, `while`, `catch`, `? :` ternary, `&&`, and `||` in a decision predicate. Inner closures/callbacks are counted as part of the containing function.

---

